@startuml seq_21_manage_notifications
title Sequence Diagram: UC-21 Manage Notifications

actor User
participant "User Web" as Frontend
participant "Notification Controller" as Controller
participant "Notification Service" as Service
participant "Notification Repo" as Repo

User -> Frontend: Open Notifications
Frontend -> Controller: GET /api/notifications
Controller -> Service: Get User Notifications
Service -> Repo: Fetch notifications for user
Repo --> Service: List of Notifications
Service --> Controller: Notifications data
Controller --> Frontend: 200 OK
Frontend --> User: Display notifications

User -> Frontend: Mark as read / Delete
Frontend -> Controller: PUT /api/notifications/{id}/read (or DELETE)
Controller -> Service: Update Notification State
Service -> Repo: Validate ownership
Repo --> Service: Ownership confirmed

alt Mark as read
    Service -> Repo: Update status to 'read'
    Repo --> Service: Updated
else Delete
    Service -> Repo: Delete notification record
    Repo --> Service: Deleted
end

Service --> Controller: Success
Controller --> Frontend: 200 OK
Frontend --> User: Update notification UI
@enduml